                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i2">
                     <note>- A prayer to be recited after the reading on <locus target="#142va">142va</locus>: ዘአቅረብኩ᎓ ማኅሌተ᎓ አዘኪርየ᎓ አዕላፈ። እምእለ᎓ ተጸምዱከ᎓ ዘልፈ…</note>
                     <note>Written in the same hand as the main text.</note>
                     <note>This prayer Za-ʾaqrabku māḥleta... is often recited after Synaxarion readings. The same prayer can be found in Mss.<ref type="mss" corresp="ESdd037">DD-037</ref>,<ref type="mss" corresp="ESfbm007">FBM-007</ref>,<ref type="mss" corresp="ESmr041">MR-041</ref>,<ref type="mss" corresp="ESfbm007">FBM-007</ref>.</note>
                     <note>- Postscript in <locus target="#142va">142va</locus>: ለዛቲ፡ መጽሐፍ፡ ስንክሳር፡ ዜና፡ መላእክት፡ ትጉሐን፨ ወተዝካረ፡ ነቢያት፡ ቅዱሳን፨ ወሰብከተ፡ ሐዋርያት፡ ፍጹማን፨ ወገድለ፡ ሰማዕታት፡ መዋዕይን። ወተዝካረ፡ ኵሎሙ፡ ጻድቃን፨ …</note>
                     <note>Written in the same hand as the main text.</note>
                  </msItem>
